1. *Čija* je ova torba? (Whose bag is this?)
2. Ona se zanima za *čiju* porodicu? (She is interested in whose family?)
3. Da li znaš *čije* je ovo auto? (Do you know whose car this is?)
4. Da li znaš *čijim* se autom moj brat vozi? (Do you know whose car my brother is driving?)
5. *Čije* je ovo novčanike? (Whose wallet is this?)
6. *Čijim* ti je poznanikom? (Whose acquaintance are you?)